            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              AI-integrated robotics designed to enhance your existing assessment workflows while enabling new automated capabilities.
            </p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/solutions" class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-royal-purple/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 block">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ’»</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">AI Software Platforms</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
