              </div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-burnt-sienna">See You at ASB 2025 in Pittsburgh</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                I'll be attending the American Society of Biomechanics Annual Meeting in Pittsburgh, mingling with fellow researchers and exploring the latest biomechanics innovations. Looking forward to connecting with the community!
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Conference Link Section -->
            <div class="pt-2 border-t border-white/10 mt-6">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-3">Conference details:</p>
              <div class="min-h-[44px] flex items-center">
                <a href="https://asbweb.org/asb-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                   class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-burnt-sienna/20 hover:bg-burnt-sienna/30 text-gray-400 py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition-all">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">ASB 2025 Website</span>
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
                </svg>
